ns and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4496, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 693918, "username": "apollo007", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/apollo007", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_mini.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_normal.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_large.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_xlarge.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_xxlarge.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_xxxlarge.png?m=1728288909", "created": 1717387944, "last_modified": 1728288909, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "sevenyangcc", "last_touched": 1781976579, "title": "周末好无聊啊！有点为退休后无事可做发愁了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1221719", "created": 1782011088, "deleted": 0, "content": "大家周末都做点啥呀？孩子老婆带着，我在家里玩电脑，玩电脑也玩的无聊了，也不知道做点啥。将来计划再过几年退休，可是退休后做啥呢？感觉更加无聊了。", "content_rendered": "<p>大家周末都做点啥呀？孩子老婆带着，我在家里玩电脑，玩电脑也玩的无聊了，也不知道做点啥。将来计划再过几年退休，可是退休后做啥呢？感觉更加无聊了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782011088, "replies": 36, "id": 1221719}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1660301119", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1660301119", "title": "分享创造", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/create", "topics": 34042, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119", "stars": 6084, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 481258, "username